            <abstract>
                <p><foreign xml:lang="gez">Wāzemā</foreign>-type <foreign xml:lang="gez">qǝne</foreign> 
                    attributed in the manuscript to a "Twoldo" who cannot be further identified.
                    It refers to <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6255LeoI">Leo I</persName> (<foreign xml:lang="gez">Lǝyon</foreign>), 
                    <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3919Eutychiu">ʾAwṭākiyos</persName> (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ʾAwṭāki</foreign>),
                    <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3591Dioscoru">Dioscorus of Alexandria</persName> (<foreign xml:lang="gez">Dǝyosqoros</foreign>), and 
                    <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3255CyrilI">Cyril I</persName> (<foreign xml:lang="gez">Qerǝllos</foreign>).
                </p>
